Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:09.99,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Bom dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.77,0:00:13.62,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Bom dia, Komichi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:27.32,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Bom dia, Erika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:33.88,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, é mesmo. Enviei as nossas fotos\Nde sábado, no lago, ao meu pai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:36.14,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Pro seu pai?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:39.90,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Ele falou que queria poder\Nter ido pescar com a gente!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:42.46,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Ele ficou surpreso com seu\Nequipamento de pesca, aliás.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.46,0:00:46.39,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,F-Ficou, é? Fico com\Num pouco de vergonha...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.39,0:00:50.27,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, e ele falou que\Nsuas mãos são lindas!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.27,0:00:51.43,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Hã?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.93,0:00:54.24,italics,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,E-Ele percebeu até isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:56.83,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Bom, você sempre cuida e\Ndeixa as suas unhas limpinhas!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.83,0:00:58.12,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Aí, eu disse a ele...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:01.21,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,...que é porque você é boa no violino!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:03.75,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,É tão legal que você sabe\Ntocar um instrumento!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:06.18,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Eu queria saber também!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.18,0:01:11.50,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Já eu acho que é muito mais incrível\Nsaber dançar, como você.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:12.83,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,É mesmo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:13.69,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.77,0:01:16.85,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Ai, vou ficar vermelhinha...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.86,0:01:24.68,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Bom dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:25.63,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Bom dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.18,0:01:27.41,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Bom dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:01.82,main,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Vamos, é hora de ir pro clube.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:04.99,sign_3520_34_Episode_One__The,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(482,1)\pos(525,70)}Episódio 7\NQuero te ouvir tocar
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:03.34,main,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Hoje foi puxado.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:04.99,main,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Vai trocar de roupa hoje?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:08.03,main,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Legal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.03,0:03:09.01,main,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Só quando terminar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:10.85,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Hebimori-san, até.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.48,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Até.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:14.91,main,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Tchau.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:15.88,top,Student,0000,0000,0000,,É o que parece.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.09,0:03:34.12,italics,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Caramba, guitarra elétrica\Né tão irado.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:37.41,main,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, qual é!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:39.24,top,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Sério, aquilo foi incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.93,main,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Faz assim de novo! Mandou muito bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:43.73,top,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Não dá, foi bem difícil!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:44.19,main,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Claro que consegue!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.19,0:03:47.13,italics,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Mas, no fim, escolhi\Nnão entrar em nenhum clube.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:04:00.20,italics,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,O quê? Ed ficou em décimo lugar?\NTá de sacanagem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:03.51,italics,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,A próxima edição terá uma matéria\Nespecial da juventude da Fukumoto Miki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:05.90,italics,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Já deu de falar da Miki, galera.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:09.34,italics,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Ai, esse modelo de guitarra\Nda Rara é tão legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:11.26,italicstop,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Se eu tivesse uma dessas, eu também...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:10.82,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hebimori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:12.68,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hebimori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.52,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hebimori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:15.77,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Boa tarde!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:20.81,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Que demais esse fone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:24.94,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,A-Akebi-san! Desculpa, não te vi aí.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:27.29,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hebimori-san, essa é...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:35.01,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,É aquela revista que pessoas\Nque fazem música leem, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:35.86,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:39.14,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Comprei uma dessas uma vez\Nporque tinha a Miki-chan na capa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:41.53,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mas quando cheguei\Nem casa e abri,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:43.52,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,só tinha partituras dentro...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:46.80,italics,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Também comprei pela capa,\Nentão nem percebi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:50.96,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Não entendi nadica\Ndo que estava escrito.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:53.82,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mas isso significa que você sabe\Ntocar algum instrumento, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:55.89,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hã? Não exatamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:59.86,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,S-Só violão...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:02.29,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,...um pouco.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:03.55,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Demais...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.98,0:05:05.57,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Eu quero te ouvir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:06.75,italics,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:09.42,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Quero te ouvir tocar violão!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:14.25,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Tudo bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:14.91,italicstop,Club President,0000,0000,0000,,Testando, testando...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:19.69,italicstop,Club President,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... Chamando Akebi Komichi,\Nda turma 1-3.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.42,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,É a presidente do meu clube!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:23.68,italicstop,Club President,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi Komichi, compareça à sala\Ndo seu clube imediatamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:22.68,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Desculpa, preciso passar no meu clube!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:25.12,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mas quero te ouvir tocar\Nalgum dia, tá?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:29.14,italicstop,Club President,0000,0000,0000,,Repetindo: Akebi Komichi,\Ncompareça à sala do seu clube—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:32.28,italics,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Agora me ferrei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:37.14,italics,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Não consigo ler partituras.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:39.65,sign_12822_113_Mangetsu_Dormito,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\an8\pos(537,270)\3c&H94AFB8&\c&H2E3B50&\blur1\1a&HFF&}Dormitório\NMangetsu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:52.04,italics,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Trouxe o violão antigo do meu pai\Nsem nenhum motivo específico.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:56.05,italics,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Bom, eu nunca o toquei\Ndesde que me mudei pra cá.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.45,italics,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Não é uma guitarra elétrica, afinal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:17.17,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.36,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,"Acordes"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:22.73,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,As notas musicais não eram\N"dó, ré, mi, fá" e assim vai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:27.73,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, achei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:30.58,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Primeiro... dó...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.31,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Vamos pro próximo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:46.16,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Consegui!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:56.30,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Bem-vinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:57.75,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Oi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:07.57,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Sempre achei que isso\Nfosse só pra decorar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.56,0:07:11.40,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, até que era, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:15.79,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, desculpa. Vou deixar pra tocar\Nquando você não estiver aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:19.12,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Tudo bem. O barulho não me incomoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:22.29,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Tá...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:42.20,italicstop,TV Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Em seguida, dobre os joelhos,\Nestique bem os braços,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:44.13,italicstop,TV Voice,0000,0000,0000,,e junte as mãos acima da cabeça.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:45.49,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Acima da cabeça!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.46,0:07:51.98,italicstop,TV Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Agora, lentamente, coloque\Na perna esquerda para frente.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.73,0:07:51.42,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,A Hebimori-san disse que\Nsabe tocar violão!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.78,sign_11281_101_Does_Hebimori_sa,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H978D8C&\3c&HF3F3F3&\pos(235,93)}Ela disse que sabe tocar violão!
