Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:52.99,sign_11281_101_Does_Hebimori_sa,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H978D8C&\3c&HDED4EB&\fad(149,1)\pos(264,52)\clip(m 389 63 l 389 57 393 51 261 51 261 62)}Ela disse que sabe tocar violão!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:52.99,sign_11281_101_Does_Hebimori_sa,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(243,10)\fscx95}A Hebimori-san toca algum instrumento?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.24,italics,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Por que você não tenta tocar\Nalguma coisa também?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.25,sign_11281_101_Does_Hebimori_sa,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(243,10)\fscx95}A Hebimori-san toca algum instrumento?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.25,sign_11281_101_Does_Hebimori_sa,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H978D8C&\3c&HDED4EB&\pos(264,52)}Ela disse que sabe tocar violão!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.25,sign_11281_101_Does_Hebimori_sa,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(240,95)\fscx85}Por que você não tenta tocar alguma coisa também?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.55,italicstop,TV Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Agora estique bem as pernas\Npara os lados,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:02.68,italicstop,TV Voice,0000,0000,0000,,e incline a coluna para a frente.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:04.37,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Música, é?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:06.34,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Pode ser legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.64,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, se concentra!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:09.54,italicstop,TV Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Agora, levante o tronco e...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:13.47,main,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,Próxima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.55,main,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,Próxima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:30.02,main,Club President,0000,0000,0000,,A, e, i, u, e, o, a, o!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:34.37,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,A, e, i, u, e, o, a, o!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.37,0:08:35.82,main,Club President,0000,0000,0000,,Mais alto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:38.03,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,A, e, i, u...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:39.42,main,Basketball Club,0000,0000,0000,,Bom trabalho por hoje.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:40.37,top,Basketball Club,0000,0000,0000,,Obrigada!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:41.35,main,Basketball Club,0000,0000,0000,,Valeu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:42.76,main,Basketball Club,0000,0000,0000,,Obrigada por hoje.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.87,main,Basketball Club,0000,0000,0000,,Obrigada!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:49.63,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,U, e, o, a, o!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:52.93,main,Club President,0000,0000,0000,,Muito bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:55.11,main,Club President,0000,0000,0000,,Isso é tudo por hoje.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:58.84,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Tá... Muito obrigada.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:01.14,main,Club President,0000,0000,0000,,Limpe esse suor antes de\Nvoltar para casa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:05.47,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Bom trabalho.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:08.23,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,T-Togano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:13.07,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi-san, você está no\NClube de Teatro, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:15.65,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Você sempre pratica aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:18.50,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Não, geralmente é na sala de aula,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:20.98,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,mas tenho praticado no pátio\Ne em outros lugares.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:22.90,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Nossa presidente disse,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:27.17,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,"A primeira coisa para melhorar é\Nusar a voz na frente das pessoas."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:29.55,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Ficou parecida.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:32.80,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Essa será a primeira vez\Nque faço uma peça,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.71,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,então ela disse que preciso\Npraticar bastante o básico.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:41.39,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Tenho treinado bastante\Nem casa... a coluna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:45.10,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Eu também tenho que me esforçar ao\Nmáximo pra acompanhar as veteranas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:46.91,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,É mesmo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:51.24,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mas é divertido quando a gente percebe que\Naos poucos aprendeu algo que não sabia, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:53.62,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:10:00.20,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Aliás, você dorme no mesmo quarto\Nque a Hebimori-san, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:00.97,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Isso mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:06.38,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Então você já deve ter ouvido ela\Ntocar violão, não é mesmo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:16.37,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Acorde G... é sol...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:18.60,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Primeira corda, terceiro traste...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:21.19,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Quinta corda, segundo traste...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:24.81,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Sexta corda, terceiro traste...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:26.46,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Pô, que difícil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:29.72,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Será que eu tô fazendo certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:34.45,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Bom, que seja. O próximo é... C, dó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.78,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Segunda corda, primeiro traste...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:39.99,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Quarta corda, segundo traste...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:43.24,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Quinta corda, terceiro traste...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.74,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,E sexta corda... abafar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:47.24,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,"Abafar"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:52.04,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Caramba, quantos acordes\Nexistem, afinal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:56.55,sign_15723_164_How_many_guitar_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(225,190)\frz0.86\t(487,488,\3c&HE3DDD5&)\fad(1,103)\fs13}Quantos acordes de violão existem?\NAcordes para leigos!
