Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:57.55,sign_15723_164_How_many_guitar_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz0.37\fad(1,103)\an1\pos(135,145)\c&HD0A28C&\3c&HEDEFEF&}Q{\c&HCFA28C&}u{\c&HCEA18B&}a{\c&HCDA08A&}n{\c&HCCA08A&}t{\c&HCB9F8A&}o{\c&HCB9E89&}s {\c&HC99E88&}a{\c&HC89D88&}c{\c&HC79C88&}o{\c&HC79C87&}r{\c&HC69C87&}d{\c&HC59B86&}e{\c&HC49A86&}s {\c&HC39A85&}d{\c&HC29985&}e {\c&HC19884&}v{\c&HC09884&}i{\c&HC09883&}o{\c&HBE9683&}l{\c&HBD9682&}ã{\c&HBC9682&}o {\c&HBB9481&}e{\c&HBA9481&}x{\c&HB99480&}i{\c&HB99380&}st{\c&HB8927F&}em{\c&HB7927F&}?{\c&HC49A86&}\N{\c&HD0A28C&\3c&HEDEFEF&}E{\c&HCFA18B&}n{\c&HCEA08B&\3c&HEDEFEE&}t{\c&HCC9E8A&\3c&HEDEEEE&}e{\c&HCB9D89&\3c&HECEEEE&}n{\c&HCA9C89&}d{\c&HC89A88&\3c&HECEEED&}e{\c&HC69987&}n{\c&HC59886&}d{\c&HC49686&\3c&HECEDEC&}o {\c&HC39585&}o{\c&HC29484&\3c&HEBEDEC&}s {\c&HC09384&}a{\c&HBF9283&\3c&HEBEDEB&}c{\c&HBE9082&\3c&HEBECEB&}o{\c&HBC8E81&\3c&HEBECEA&}r{\c&HBA8D81&}d{\c&HB98C80&\3c&HEAECEA&}e{\c&HB78A7F&\3c&HEAECE9&}s{\c&HB6887E&\3c&HEAEBE9&}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:01.18,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Tá brincando.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:04.67,italics,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Bom, eu nunca vou usar\Ntodos eles, mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:07.28,italics,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Se eu aprender só os importantes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:19.95,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Bem-vinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:21.65,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Oi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:25.82,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Togano-san, você comentou outro dia\Nque gosta desse jogo, não?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:31.59,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Encontrei com a Akebi-san\Ndepois do clube.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:33.44,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah, é?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:37.74,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Ela disse que está doida\Npra te ouvir tocar violão.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:40.50,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Você não vai tocar hoje?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:45.55,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Parece que há vários jeitos\Nde tocar violão, sabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.11,0:11:51.05,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,E muitos usam letras do\Nalfabeto, como C e E.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:54.17,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,E eu tô apanhando pra seguir as aulas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:56.73,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,É impossível eu aprender\Na tocar violão.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:12:00.33,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Então não deveria dizer isso\Npra Akebi-san logo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:07.38,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Eu virei aquele parafusão\Ne uma corda arrebentou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:10.32,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Bom, elas estavam bem enferrujadas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:11.70,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:15.66,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Mas isso só mostra que eu\Nsou uma novata nisso tudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:16.75,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,E o que você vai fazer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:21.44,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Bom, quero aprender a tocar,\Nmas vendo a situação...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:24.18,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Acho que é tarde demais\Npra começar agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:26.69,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Ninguém domina algo\Nde uma hora pra outra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:31.52,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,É por isso que eu pratico todos os dias.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:41.15,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Venci de novo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:44.74,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Togano-san, você é muito boa nisso.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.71,main,Tennis Club,0000,0000,0000,,Boa! Joga pra cá!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:51.71,top,Tennis Club,0000,0000,0000,,Isso aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:53.09,main,Tennis Club,0000,0000,0000,,Isso, mexam essas pernas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.09,0:12:53.88,main,Tennis Club,0000,0000,0000,,Mais uma vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:54.72,main,Tennis Club,0000,0000,0000,,Boa tacada!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:04.99,italics,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,A Tatsumori-san está\Nno clube de atletismo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:09.30,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,A, e, i, u, e, o, a, o!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.01,top,Club President,0000,0000,0000,,Muito bem, Akebi Komichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:14.16,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,A, e, i, u, e, o, a, o!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:14.16,top,Club President,0000,0000,0000,,A voz tem que vir do abdome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:18.57,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,A, e, i, u, e, o, a, o!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:16.28,italicstop,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:21.30,top,Club President,0000,0000,0000,,Está melhor do que estava ontem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:23.98,italics,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Olha o quanto ela está suando...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:23.43,top,Club President,0000,0000,0000,,Vamos manter esse ritmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:24.30,top,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Tá!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:26.66,italics,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Mas ela parece meio...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:50.94,main,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,Boa, Togano. No próximo treino,\Nvocê ficará de ala.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:51.48,main,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Entendido!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:53.72,italics,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,A Togano-san, também.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:05.01,main,Oshizu,0000,0000,0000,,Consegui!
